<item>
            <title>[LU-13595] add option to lustre_rmmod to dump debug logs</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-13595</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;It would be convenient for &lt;tt&gt;lustre_rmmod&lt;/tt&gt; to have an option like &quot;&lt;tt&gt;--debug-kernel|-d&lt;/tt&gt;&quot; to dump the kernel debug logs before the libcfs module is unloaded.  This would facilitate log collection related to memory allocation (if &lt;tt&gt;+malloc&lt;/tt&gt; debugging is enabled), or subsystem cleanup.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
